name: Water Butt
tag: rain water store collect storage structure
desc: Collect your rain water by connecting the tube on the storage container to your roof gutter down pipe. Choose one with a base if you need to raise the container and tap to the correct height for filling a watering can. Optionally the overflow can be connected to another container.

name: Water cube
tag: rain water store collect storage structure
desc: Reuse a water tight container or add some pond liner to a weatherproof container. It needs to be large enough so that some water remains liquid even if the top freezes, usually 60cm deep is enough.
